Class Itemsets

  • java.lang.Object
    • Charm_BitSet.Itemsets
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Itemsets
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a set of itemsets. They are ordered by size. For example, level 1 means itemsets of size 1 (that contains 1 item).
